'''Drallish''' was the official [[Language/Legends|language]] of [[Drall (planet)|Drall]], used by its native [[Species/Legends|species]], also known as [[Drall/Legends|Drall]].<ref name="u">''[[Ultimate Alien Anthology]]''</ref>

Most Dralls were learned in [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]] too.<ref name="u" /> ''Sha'lott'' was a Drallish word that meant "graywing."<ref name="CatCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

